Isaa isa kadhannaan isaan irraa akka qeebaluu dideefi
fedhii isaanii isaaniif fiixaan hin baasin nutti himeera.
gaafatu kan Muhammad  guyyaa Badrii Rabbii isaanii
gaafatan kadhatan caalu hin dhageenye: “yaa Rabbi ani
waan ati naaf wareegdeenin si guya’a’ jedhan.”
uumamniifi wanti isa keessa jiru hunduu kan Rabbiiti.
